---
title: Seared Scallop, Lemon and Pea Oven-Baked Risotto with Leek and Pumpkin Seed & Rocket Salad
description: This Seared Scallop, Lemon and Pea Oven-Baked Risotto takes inspiration from classic restaurant dishes with a gourmet protein to bring a fine dining experience straight into your home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R32_W46_UK_SPP22194-4_Main_13_high-5ec7050f.jpg
